name: UnofficialInstagramCaptions
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: unofficial instagram captions
des: Don't know what caption fits with your post? Don't worry, all you have to say is 'Alexa, open unofficial instagram captions'. Alexa will give a wide range of fun, quirky and unique captions that will definitely fetch more likes. Keep saying 'next' for more cool captions. You can say help at any point and stop to exit.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
